name: I JUST WANNA GO HOME
description:
Your a socially awkward recluse who’s been dragged to a party by your friend Jimmy.

However, Jimmy isn’t there, so you need to find a way out by going deeper and deeper into the party your trying to leave.(Of course, you could just leave but then everyone will hate you!)

6 unique and WHACKY endings to discover (Plus 1 secret one), which can you achieve?Controls: WASD to move E to interact Q to drop items Spacebar to CONSUME certain items
